2017-05-10
		rgpio -- Raspberry Pi GPIO Tool
		-------------------------------

This is the "rgpio" command.
Runs on Raspberry Pi (RPi) to read/control the GPIO configuration.

Revision control:  git

Files:  (2020-08-30)
------
README			this file

.gitignore		Git ignore transient files

